#~ "A plugin, which does zen-coding like selector completion. For more "
#~ "information see <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zen_Coding\"> "
#~ "Zen Coding</ulink>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Priedas, kuris daro zen-coding tipo teksto pakeitimus. Daugiau "
#~ "informacijos rasite <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zen_Coding"
#~ "\">Zen Coding straipsnyje</ulink>."
